drink after stabbing and killing a patron at a tavern in central Joburg has
been arrested."The victim and the suspect had an argument while
drinking in the tavern. He pulled out the knife, stabbed the victim and dragged
him outside the tavern," said Captain Xoli Mbele."Police were contacted and found the suspect inside
